------------------

Port Notes:

----- version 0.8.7-1 -----
Version bump.

----- version 0.8.6-1 -----
Upstream version bump.

----- version 0.8.5-1 -----
Version bump; package now called libIDL2 to make space for the libIDL
included in ORBit-0.5.

The libIDL.m4 aclocal macro file is no longer included, as it conficts 
with the same file from the libIDL included in ORBit-0.5.
pkg-config should be used instead.

----- version 0.8.3-2 -----
This build includes libIDL.m4, with the fix for the underquoted aclocal 
warning; this is the equivalent of upstream 0.8.4.

----- version 0.8.3-1 -----
Initial release for Cygwin.


Cygwin port maintained by:
http://cygwinports.dotsrc.org/
